item.description:
@ohokay wrote:

Well I don’t know whether it was you who followed the tutorial wrong, or the guy who made it, but something went wrong. Basically everything you pasted in the ClickingButtons class, is trying to access other variables and methods which are supposed to be located in client, and they’re not there.
